        <p class="pdet__ing-row"><strong>Why we selected it:</strong> Widely used in skin-focused gel formulations for its ability to help the appearance of skin texture appear more even over time.</p>
        <p class="pdet__ing-row"><strong>What you'll notice:</strong> A smooth, comfortable feel with no greasy residue.</p>
