        </button>
        <div class="pfaq__a" id="pfaq-silken-2"><p>Yes. Silken is suited to both recently healed and long-standing scars, used consistently as part of your routine.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pfaq__item">
        <button type="button" class="pfaq__q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pfaq-silken-3">
