      </div>
      <div class="pfaq__item">
        <button type="button" class="pfaq__q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pfaq-silken-5">
          <span>How long should I use Silken?</span>
          <span class="pfaq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pfaq__a" id="pfaq-silken-5"><p>Consistency is what Silken is built for. Most people incorporate it into their daily routine for an extended period, applying it every morning and evening as part of their ritual.</p></div>
