        <button type="button" class="pfaq__q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pfaq-silken-8">
          <span>Will Silken feel greasy?</span>
          <span class="pfaq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="pfaq__a" id="pfaq-silken-8"><p>No — Silken is a lightweight, silky gel designed to absorb into a breathable, non-greasy finish.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pfaq__item">
        <button type="button" class="pfaq__q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pfaq-silken-9">
          <span>Can I use Silken on sensitive skin?</span>
          <span class="pfaq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
